Please download the JS8Spotter DB Upgrade Tool to migrate an old database file to work with the
latest version of Spotter. The tool is available on KF7MIX.com.

(As of v1.14, database upgrade requirements will be listed here, latest first)

v1.17 -> v1.18      No database upgrade needed
v1.16 -> v1.17      DATABASE UPDATE REQUIRED
v1.15 -> v1.16      DATABASE UPDATE REQUIRED
v1.14 -> v1.15      No database upgrade needed
v1.13 -> v1.14      No database upgrade needed
